items.comment:
Hey Michael,

Did you have this beer today? We released this IPA 8 months ago. Ambervale shouldnt have it on tap
White Bay Beer Co. Hey there, yes it was on tap. Number 7 on their tap list found under the Ambervale page here on untapped. Is the beer not it's best?
They purchased that keg in December, theres no reason it shouldve been on tap. Were going to collect the keg this week.
Well also reconsider selling them any of our beer in the future as this is unacceptable. You should ask for your money back.
